insert into fato_pocco(id_regiao, id_item_type,id_sales_channel,id_order_priority,order_date, id_orders,ship_date,units_sold,unit_price,unit_cost,total_revenue,total_cost,total_profit,id_country, times_temp) select distinct r.id, a.id, v.id, p.id, date_format(str_to_date(o.order_date, '%m/%d/%Y'), '%Y-%m-%d'),o.id_orders ,date_format(str_to_date(o.ship_date, '%m/%d/%Y'), '%Y-%m-%d'),units_sold,o.unit_price,o.unit_cost,o.total_revenue,o.total_cost,o.total_profit,c.id, current_timestamp() from nifi001.orders o inner join dm_regiao r on o.regiao = r.regiao inner join dm_item_type a on o.item_type =a.item_type inner join dm_sales_channel v on o.sales_channel= v.sales_channel inner join dm_order_priority p on o.order_priority = p.order_priority inner join dm_country c on o.country= c.country;
